reviewText: This was a gift for grandson. I selected it from Amazon reviews.  I don't know if he liked it.  magarrity

I didn't expect much when I first decided to purchase this documentary so when I was done watching it I was very happy with my purchase.  This isn't a randomly put-together documentary.  It was well thought out and really tributes basketball in America.  A must see for basketball players, coaches and enthusiasts.
